Lifelong learning is crucial to success On average, each employee spent about 30 hours in digital

learning or on-site trainings during the fiscal year. Our new training opportunities and learning week promotions resulted in an increase in the number of training hours in fiscal 2023.

In fiscal 2023, Siemens invested €237 million in our people’s training, which corresponds to an average of €753 per employee. In total, we invested approximately €416 million in employee education and training.